{"type":"article","id":13505,"title":"豆瓣读书花千芳著作《做一个幸福的中国人》留言集体翻车","uid":749,"topics":[1,2913],"contents":"无意间在豆瓣上找到这本书，发现评价完全大翻车，看来民智已开。<br>\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3c326c898f34b09a046fd.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3c326c898f34b09a046fd.png\" alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3c326c898f34b09a046fd.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9d4f2c4b1b424e9846c5d.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9d4f2c4b1b424e9846c5d.png\" alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9d4f2c4b1b424e9846c5d.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/file/aa97ded307d27ac22a8da.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/aa97ded307d27ac22a8da.png\" alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/aa97ded307d27ac22a8da.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<b>第一条留言写的很好，人和狗的区别论述的很好。</b><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9ccdbad01548982ec4902.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9ccdbad01548982ec4902.png\" alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9ccdbad01548982ec4902.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ec2de54082a07f968677a.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ec2de54082a07f968677a.png\" alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ec2de54082a07f968677a.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n我其实很惊讶为什么豆瓣没有关闭这本书的评价，豆瓣就把周小平的《请不要辜负这个时代》的评价功能关闭了。看来花千芳在党国眼里，没有周小平重要。不过也有一种说法，周小平是装疯，花千芳是真疯，党国可能也认为花千芳没救了。哈哈","date":"2020-02-01","agreeCount":26,"discussionCount":0}